res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/kqtz1e37t4yetpylsitz 117w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/twup4exgwrytrrm12xty 197w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/ywsnxgi4jkdgzzkaywca 277w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/pwgzegwjpchng5awwamr 357w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/l91p8w6cns1vwv45vbnx 437w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/f0clzb0grkntf4yoaiwn 517w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/svggptsdcakpa5rqluyt 597w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/cnu3zkpjnqgsobreuti0 677w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/sr94uqwukzxi8eveetoe 757w"><br>取<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="N"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.085em;">N</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>为除了你之外参与这个药丸游戏的人数。我假设<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="N"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.085em;">N</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>很大，所以选择蓝色的<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>数量大约为<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="xN"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.085em;">N</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 。我还将假设<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="N"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.085em;">N</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>是偶数，因此玩家总数是奇数，以避免必须猜测平局时会发生什么。</p><p>现在，考虑你的效用函数。我们可以首先假设它是线性的<span class="footnote-reference" role="doc-noteref" id="fnrefs4iy3ko6k4e"><sup><a href="#fns4iy3ko6k4e">[1]</a></sup></span> ，并且您平等地重视其他人的生命，但其价值是您自己生命的<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\nu"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.036em;">ν</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>倍（遵循 Ege Erdil 的命名法以保持一致性）。然后，缩放使你自己的生命值为 1，我们可以在玩之前定义你的效用：</p> <span><span class="mjpage mjpage__block"><span class="mjx-chtml MJXc-display" style="text-align: center;"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="U_{init} = \nu N + 1"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.084em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.084em;">U</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">i</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">i</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">t</span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.036em;">ν</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.085em;">N</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">+</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><p>您还可以为红色选择者和蓝色选择者分配不同的值（我看到的一位评论者说他们不想生活在一个只有选择红色的人的世界中），但我现在将忽略这个复杂性。</p><p>现在，如果<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\nu=0"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.036em;">ν</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mj