mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">&lt;</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.085em;">N</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">/</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，同样作为对<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="x"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>的期望。在这里我将使用<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="B = xN"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.085em;">N</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>的近似值。那么<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="B < N/2"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">&lt;</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.085em;">N</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">/</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span>的</span></span></span></span></span>预期概率就是 beta 分布的 CDF 高达 0.5。此近似对于<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="N"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.085em;">N</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>值大于几百时有效： </p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:68.23%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/dmdihfyt6smeufnlcl5x" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/rp5gw2fi7gufjplcrq0k 210w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/hhokx9mftluf5psemdlz 420w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/jrfhymcrewrwczyhzhzn 630w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/ui9lwbbjqdsdwzgtbfi5 840w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/mjx3ndg5eewlgpqem6v4 1050w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/lmwkbeni9xrmlvkojglz 1260w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/oitfqzvucrvjzgxsmhs8 1470w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/bixiatqyomcafilyb3dy 1680w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/lfmkhouwendur45jfmzy 1890w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/y3hwolaeytpynonthbgu 2028w"></figure><p>这意味着对于我们上面的后验，如果你选择蓝色，大多数人选择红色的概率约为 0.1817。如果你选择红色，则相反：大多数人选择红色的概率为 1-0.1817 = 0.8183，高出 4 倍多。</p><p>我们需要计算的最后一件事是，在大多数人选择红色的情况下，我们应该预期死亡的玩家数量。这种考虑将推向相反的方向。如果你选择了蓝色，那么大多数人很可能也选择了蓝色——但如果蓝色没有达到大多数人的选择，那么它可能会有点少。这意味着更多的死亡。</p><p>具体来说，我们想要<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="x"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>在区间 (0, 0.5) 上的期望。下图中的虚线显示了这一点。你可以粗略地看到，它们每个人都将绿色区域分成两半。对于您选择红色的情况，死亡玩家的预期比例（以红色多数为条件）为 0.1527。如果您选择蓝色，则为 0.3120，大约是其两倍。 </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/a8le8kmscoo10gd0iwyn" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/lgcntmvfkp810uhzjkbj 280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/zcyftn4kc3fhxeo2uhka 560w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/s7zh2z3bxulvccwybkoo 840w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/jpqnoz4eznsfldlg97ps 1120w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/sjjlx0e5rahoheghcvk0 1400w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/vvuuss8uewqrkqmvomp6 1680w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/zxykd5oog0wnhuxuixic 1960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/ibgqi6bgzwsknyqiafmh 2240w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/ydepmmgvnwp2fou7c6au 2520w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/lsaolwzvfuxrputojkn5 2779w"><figcaption>虚线显示如果大多数人选择红色，则死亡玩家（选择蓝色）的预期比例。 (a) 如果您选择红色，您应该期待什么，(b) 如果您选择蓝色，您应该期待什么</figcaption></figure><p>现在我们可以返回并计算每种情况的预期效用函数：</p><p> <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mathbb{E}[U_{blue}] = (1-0.1817)(\nu N + 1) + 0.1817(\nu N (1-0.3120)) + \mathbb{P}_{tiebreaker}(\nu N+1)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-ams-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">E</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">[</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.084em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.084em;">U</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.219em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="paddin